Date: Mon, 25 Aug 2025 10:42:24 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 6/9] bgpd: install srv6 encap nexhtop
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Like others srv6 service, check the sid for the nexthop tracking and
allow install route using sid as nexhtop at the reception.

Signed-off-by: Loïc Sang <loic.sang@6wind.com>
