From 15b8f7deed1cd0e391e53c2243174ec81b503c52 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?Lo=C3=AFc=20Sang?= <loic.sang@6wind.com>
Date: Wed, 20 Aug 2025 17:47:35 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 7/9] topotests: add bgp srv6 unicast topotests
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Test bgp srv6 unicast tests on default vrf. The topo consist of 4
routers:
1. R1 <-> R2, R1 is peering with encapsulation-srv6-relax enabled
2. R1 <-> R3, R1 and R3 are peering with encapsulation-srv6 enabled
3. R1 <-> R4, normal bgp peering.
4. "sid export auto"" command is activated on R1 and R3
5. C1 and cC are both client to test datapath:
c1 <-> R2 <-> R1 <-> R3 <-> c2

Tests are:
- test_bgp_srv6_encap: static network 10.0.0.1/32 is configured on R1,
  check route on R2, R3 and R4.
- test_bgp_srv6_update1: static network 10.0.0.2/32 is configured on R2,
  check route on R3 and R4.
- test_bgp_srv6_update2: static network 10.0.0.3/32 is configured on R3,
  check rotue on R1, R2 and R4.
- test_bgp_srv6_sid_rmap: check prefix 172.16.0.0/24 is filtered.
- test_bgp_srv6_sid_unexport: unexport sid, check route on R2-R3.
- test_bgp_srv_sid_export: re-enabled sid export, check srv6 encap
  routes are re-installed.
- test_bgp_srv6_sid_v6_update: check srv6 ipv6 unicast sid allocation
  adn updates.
- test_srv6_withdraw: withdraw ipv4 and ipv6 prefixes and check routes
  are uninstalled.
- test_ping: check c1 <-> c2 pings.

Signed-off-by: Loïc Sang <loic.sang@6wind.com>
